      "content": "that's a great start, really captures the tone. can u expand on that? maybe have him write about why he thinks the local culture and traditions actually hold the people back? like, how he views their customs as something that needs to be replaced by British values to make them more \"advanced.\" just want to lean into that sense of duty he feels.",
